data.description: Step foot into this beautiful 3800+ square foot house in desirable Weybridge Chase and you'll know you are truly home. The double door entryway leads to a soaring, two-story, 15x11 foot foyer showcasing a beautiful staircase and maple hardwood flooring. To the left is the living room, complete with bay window and custom pillars. Beyond the pillars is a large, formal dining room accented with crown molding and perfect for entertaining guests in style. A chef's dream kitchen awaits with custom maple cabinetry, granite center island, stainless steel appliances, a double oven, recessed lighting, ceramic tile floor, and backsplash. Sip your morning coffee in the breakfast/sunroom that overlooks the impeccable backyard and leads out to the patio. A home office is conveniently located off of the foyer. Relax by the gas fireplace in the family room,set off the kitchen, with its two-story wall of windows letting in natural light. A custom staircase from the family room leads to the upstairs where four spacious bedrooms and three full bathrooms await. Forget all your cares in the oversized master suite where you'll be swept away by the cathedral ceilings, a three-sided gas fireplace, his and her walk-in closets, gorgeous hardwood floors, dressing area and a sitting area perfect for curling up with a novel. An oversized bath with its custom vanity and whirlpool tub completes the master suite. One bedroom is a princess suite and has its own bath while the two remaining bedrooms share the hall bath. A full finished basement with a half bath and a large storage area affords the perfect location for entertaining guests or watching movies. Unwind in paradise on the immaculate paver patio overlooking the expansive and lush backyard. Never worry again about power outages because this home offers a full-house generator. Step outside to the beautiful backyard with an in-ground sprinkler system. With a 1 acre lot there is plenty of room for fun. An extra-wide driveway and three-car garage round out this executive home.  Take advantage of this chance to secure a home below market value and add the finishing touches into your dream residence.
